      <title>委内瑞拉地震袭击了已经陷入危机的卫生系统</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/26/world/americas/venezuela-earthquake-shortages-doctors.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名医生表示，由于手电筒短缺，消防队员只能使用手机灯，灾区一家不堪重负的医院在没有自来水的情况下运转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/26/world/americas/venezuela-earthquake-shortages-doctors.html</guid>
